Package com.github.rholder.fauxflake

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    DefaultIdGenerator
    This is the default reference implementation of the IdGenerator interface that is resilient enough to handle leap seconds, however, backwards time that occurs when the system time is updated, as from NTP, will result in an InterruptedException.
    DefaultIdGenerator.Values
    This is a simple tuple-y pair class.
    EncodedId
    Use an EncodingProvider to back an implementation of the Id interface.
    IdGenerators
    This class provides a collection of convenience methods for constructing common IdGenerator implementations.
